      "span_text": "A gene encoding a potassium transporter from N. rustica (NrHAK1), known to be responsive to potassium starvation, was used as positive control in the deprivation assays (primers 5′GCA GAG GAT ATT CAA CAT TCAG3′ and 5′CCA CCT TCA CCA TTA TCA TCAG3′)."
